description: Serving LOS ANGELES, ORANGE COUNTY, RIVERSIDE, and SAN BERNARDINO. One of the most UNIQUE Food Trucks on the Streets Simply reinvented old fare in a new way with bold taste, that's right. And our mission, to consistently raise the bar of street food concept by offering eclectic infused flavors from the coast of Baja to the Far East, BAJIAN for short.  Inspired by both invigorating and organic ingredients, prepared fresh on site, cooked to order, clean, and fast while providing service excellence to our customers.
name: Street Foods Co
